  <entry>
    <title>PVE 安装寄</title>
    <link href="http://blog.shira-aya.top/posts/pve-an-zhuang-ji-946669ad/"/>
    <id>http://blog.shira-aya.top/posts/pve-an-zhuang-ji-946669ad/</id>
    <published>2023-01-18T23:03:03.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-01-20T06:09:44.569Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>脑袋一热，今天理线的时候想灌个 PVE 玩。于是就去灌了。  </p><span id="more"></span><p>PVE, 也就是<a href="https://www.proxmox.com/en/proxmox-ve">Proxmox VE</a>，是一个完整的开源的服务器管理平台，用于虚拟化。</p><h2 id="1-准备"><a href="#1-准备" class="headerlink" title="1. 准备"></a>1. 准备</h2><p>下载最新的 PVE 在 <a href="https://www.proxmox.com/en/proxmox-ve">这里</a><br>用你的方法放到 U 盘里面，用于安装。我选用 <a href="https://www.ventoy.net/cn/index.html">Ventoy</a> 工具直接把 iso 丢进去，非常方便。  </p><h2 id="2-安装"><a href="#2-安装" class="headerlink" title="2. 安装"></a>2. 安装</h2><p>安装是简单的，插上 U 盘，插上键盘鼠标，进入安装镜像，照着提示装就是了。  </p><h2 id="3-配置"><a href="#3-配置" class="headerlink" title="3. 配置"></a>3. 配置</h2><p>在电脑上登入 <code>http://192.168.xxx.xxx:8006</code>, 进入 PVE 的管理界面。  </p><p><img src="/posts/pve-an-zhuang-ji-946669ad/2023-01-19-15-21-27.png" alt=" "><br>进入如图所示的Shell界面。</p><h3 id="1-禁用企业源"><a href="#1-禁用企业源" class="headerlink" title="1) 禁用企业源"></a>1) 禁用企业源</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell"><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;#deb https://enterprise.proxmox.com/debian/pve bullseye pve-enterprise&quot;</span> &gt; /etc/apt/sources.list.d/pve-enterprise.list</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-换国内源"><a href="#2-换国内源" class="headerlink" title="2) 换国内源"></a>2) 换国内源</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><figcaption><span>/etc/apt/sources.list</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment">#deb http://ftp.debian.org/debian bullseye main contrib</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#deb http://ftp.debian.org/debian bullseye-updates main contrib</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># security updates</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#deb http://security.debian.org bullseye/updates main contrib</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># debian aliyun source</span><br>deb https://mirrors.aliyun.com/debian bullseye main contrib non-free<br>deb https://mirrors.aliyun.com/debian bullseye-updates main contrib non-free<br>deb https://mirrors.aliyun.com/debian bullseye/updates main contrib non-free<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># proxmox source</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># deb http://download.proxmox.com/debian/pve bullseye pve-no-subscription</span><br>deb https://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/proxmox/debian/pve bullseye pve-no-subscription<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell"><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;deb https://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/proxmox/debian/pve bullseye pve-no-subscription&quot;</span> &gt; /etc/apt/sources.list.d/pve-no-subscription.list</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>最后，再 <code>apt update</code> 一下，就装到能用的水准了。  </p>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;脑袋一热，今天理线的时候想灌个 PVE 玩。于是就去灌了。  &lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
